We match [notmuch's C
style](https://git.notmuchmail.org/git?p=notmuch;a=blob_plain;f=devel/STYLE;hb=HEAD).
Well, actually we match their [uncrustify.cfg](uncrustify.cfg), and endeavour
not to fiddle beyond that. An automated style-format is preferred, even when it
could be minorly improved with manual changes.
